sources.title: Batton Story (1976, italian film) Comedy, Drama | Directed by Mario Landi
sources.description:
When injustice sparked a movement
Femi is accused of being a prostitute and is thrown into jail with the rest of the clan. There she befriends the prostitutes and decides to set up an organization for prostitutes' rights.

Original title: Le impiegate stradali (1976) AKA: Batton Story 

Uncensored version: https://youtu.be/rBTaGSsC71w


This film is available with Italian audio, and subtitled in many lanugages

Director: Mario Landi
Writer: Piero Regnoli
Cast: Femi Benussi, Marisa Merlini, Daniela Giordano
Genres: Italian cinema, Comedy, Drama, Foreign Film
